If your daughter hadn't
taken our son to row the boat,

362
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:33,800
would my wife have lost her life?

363
00:19:33,840 --> 00:19:34,960
How was that possible?

364
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:36,560
