372
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:49,480
And the boat overturned.

373
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:51,720
My sister-in-law
drowned while trying to save them.

374
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:52,720
It's all her fault.

375
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:54,560
She caused the
death of my sister-in-law.

376
00:19:54,560 --> 00:19:55,560
You're talking nonsense.

377
00:19:56,040 --> 00:19:57,280
He's just a child.

378
00:19:57,280 --> 00:19:58,640
How can you believe a child's words?

379
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,280
Then ask your daughter.

380
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:02,400
Tong,

381
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:04,600
