382
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:07,280
Stop crying.

383
00:20:07,560 --> 00:20:08,640
Speak up.

384
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,680
Tell them.

385
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,840
Shall we call that an admission?

386
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:12,960
Admitting what?

387
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:14,760
My daughter is innocent.

388
00:20:14,760 --> 00:20:17,040
Who will bring back the life of my wife?

389
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:18,600
My daughter is innocent.

390
00:20:18,600 --> 00:20:21,000
What does my
daughter have to do with this?

391
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,440
What did you say?

392
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:24,760
Don't go in.

393
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:26,240
What are you doing?

394
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:29,360
You were running
a fever for several days.

395
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:31,600
When you woke up,
you didn't remember anything.

396
00:20:32,360 --> 00:20:35,040
The doctor called it selective amnesia.

397
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,560
Which means forgetting the past.

398
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:39,800
I didn't want
to see you get hurt any more,

399
00:20:40,680 --> 00:20:42,160
so I blocked the news.

400
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:44,000
I lied to you,

401
00:20:44,200 --> 00:20:46,040
saying that your
mom died in a car accident.

402
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:51,560
Why are you only telling me now?

403
00:20:53,960 --> 00:20:55,120
Don't you understand?

404
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:57,560
The deeper your feelings for her now,

405
00:20:57,640 --> 00:20:59,560
