the truth will be for you.

406
00:20:59,840 --> 00:21:01,280
I'm doing this for your own good.

407
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:10,000
Yanxu.

408
00:21:12,360 --> 00:21:13,040
Your head...

409
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:14,160
What's wrong with your head?

410
00:21:14,320 --> 00:21:14,960
Yanxu.

411
00:21:15,360 --> 00:21:17,080
Let's go rowing.

412
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:19,560
Come.

413
00:21:19,560 --> 00:21:21,080
Give me your hand.

414
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,160
What happened to your head?

415
00:21:24,080 --> 00:21:24,880
Tell daddy.

416
00:21:26,320 --> 00:21:27,120
Yanxu.

417
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:42,680
Have you arrived home, Yanxu?

418
00:21:44,080 --> 00:21:45,640
Is your dad okay?

419
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:54,680
Call me back when you're available.

