442
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:35,360
I'm not a screenwriter.

443
00:23:36,360 --> 00:23:37,160
No such thing.

444
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:37,960
Okay.

445
00:23:38,680 --> 00:23:39,920
